到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T23:04:24.000Z","msg":"假設每年年尾計息一次<br />\n計左25年之後有幾多錢先<br />\n第一年年尾 入1000 變左 1000*(1+0.04)^25<br />\n第二年年尾 入1000 變左 1000*(1+0.04)^24<br />\n.....<br />\n第廿四年年尾 入1000 變左1000*(1+0.04)^2<br />\n最後第廿五年 入1000 變左1000*(1+0.04)<br />\nSum of gs 計總數 T<br />\n總共拎12次錢 12W<br />\n因為每年都仲計梗息<br />\n所以第一年拎完錢之後得返 (T-2W)*1.04<br />\n第二年{[(T-2W)*1.04]-2W}*1.04<br />\n.....<br />\n第十年 太長唔想寫了"},{"pid":"be26c4bdc712190bcdd4e5c3793894198e17b4e9","tid":846943,"uid":167882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11c11106b5aa4b6a1c66a442d33b844c3d170aa","tid":846943,"uid":51164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d65880b4aceebc590d87e24ae2ddd82bcf8e006","tid":846943,"uid":167882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4990ae30e93274a6d55b2c7d23b0a6a3525b8d6","tid":846943,"uid":83194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:39:48.000Z","msg":"C/r+(1-1/(1+r)^n)<br />\n功課自己做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:41:10.000Z","msg":"依條式都用唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T23:04:24.000Z","msg":"假設每年年尾計息一次<br />\n計左25年之後有幾多錢先<br />\n第一年年尾 入1000 變左 1000*(1+0.04)^25<br />\n第二年年尾 入1000 變左 1000*(1+0.04)^24<br />\n.....<br />\n第廿四年年尾 入1000 變左1000*(1+0.04)^2<br />\n最後第廿五年 入1000 變左1000*(1+0.04)<br />\nSum of gs 計總數 T<br />\n總共拎12次錢 12W<br />\n因為每年都仲計梗息<br />\n所以第一年拎完錢之後得返 (T-2W)*1.04<br />\n第二年{[(T-2W)*1.04]-2W}*1.04<br />\n.....<br />\n第十年 太長唔想寫了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T23:12:02.000Z","msg":"但係佢半年一次咁個rate應該會變？"},{"pid":"21d0344b4f7f653ee18772d4e7128960f1f09a19","tid":846943,"uid":83194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d65880b4aceebc590d87e24ae2ddd82bcf8e006","tid":846943,"uid":167882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4990ae30e93274a6d55b2c7d23b0a6a3525b8d6","tid":846943,"uid":83194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13871178694942419a3add96987b1c0f28e10e53","tid":846943,"uid":167882,"li